ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectOrder Authorizing to sign, execute and issue an Instrument of Full Powers, subject to ratification, the Agreement between the Government of Canada and the Government of the Commonwealth of The Bahamas on Air Transport
PrecisOrder Authorizing (a) the Prime Minister or the Minister of Foreign Affairs to sign, on behalf of the Government of Canada, subject to ratification, the AGREEMENT BETWEEN THE GOVERNMENT OF CANADA AND THE GOVERNMENT OF THE COMMONWEALTH OF THE BAHAMAS ON AIR TRANSPORT; or (b) the Minister of Foreign Affairs to execute and issue an Instrument of Full Powers authorizing the individuals mentioned in the order, to sign, on behalf of the Government of Canada, subject to ratification, the AGREEMENT BETWEEN THE GOVERNMENT OF CANADA AND THE GOVERNMENT OF THE COMMONWEALTH OF THE BAHAMAS ON AIR TRANSPORT.
